 for $\\sim$ 1\nMyr before being restored. This highly variable UV field will influence the\nphotoevaporation of protoplanetary discs near massive stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Jun 2019 17:59:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-26"}
