ing\nof such dynamics in MI. These results suggest that distinct dynamic structures,\ndetected with different sensitivity by nonlinear measures, lie beneath\nshort-term HRV in different physiological states and pathological conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Jun 2019 20:33:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
