 is also suspected\nthat the hadronic matter may not be far from the (nearly) perfect fluid nature\nlike the quark gluon plasma.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Jun 2019 05:32:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-01"}
