onstrated. Moreover, the possibility of\nelectron acceleration to tens of MeV with millijoule level THz pulses is\ntheoretically shown. The final goal of the above studies is a fully THz-driven\ncompact light source facility, whose start-to-end simulation is fulfilled in\nthis thesis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Jun 2019 16:46:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-17"}
