ize to the temporal domain. We\ndemonstrate superior performance on three challenging large scale affect\nestimation datasets, AffectNet, SEWA, and AFEW-VA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Jun 2019 13:30:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 Mar 2020 23:57:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-02"}
